[0.068, "o", "\u001b[0;1;31m×\u001b[0m mariadb.service - MariaDB 12.3.2 database server\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://advan/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n    Drop-In: /usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d\r\n             └─\u001b]8;;file://advan/usr/lib/systemd/system/mariadb.service.d/galera.conf\u001b\\galera.conf\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n     Active: \u001b[0;1;31mfailed\u001b[0m (Result: exit-code) since Sun 2026-06-07 13:19:32 UTC; 6min ago\r\n Invocation: 577730073221451fb3baeac2f82c2b8f\r\n       Docs: \u001b]8;;man:mariadbd(8)\u001b\\man:mariadbd(8)\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n             \u001b]8;;https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b\\https://mariadb.com/kb/en/library/systemd/\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n    Process: 1363 ExecStartPre=/bin/sh -c [ ! -e /usr/bin/galera_recovery ] && VAR= ||   VAR=`/usr/bin/galera_recovery`; [ $? -eq 0 ]   && echo _WSREP_START_POSITION=$VAR > /run/mariadb/wsrep-start-position || exit 1 (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n    Process: 1389 ExecStart=/usr/bin/mariadbd $MYSQLD_OPTS $_WSREP_NEW_CLUSTER $_WSREP_START_POSITION \u001b[0;1;31m(code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\u001b[0m\r\n   Main PID: 1389 (code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)\r\n     Status: \"\u001b[0;1;36mMariaDB server is down\u001b[0m\"\r\n   Mem peak: 94.1M\r\n        CPU: 2.498s\r\n\r\nJun 07 13:19:30 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:30 0 [Note] InnoDB: Buffer pool(s) load completed at 260607 13:19:30\r\nJun 07 13:19:30 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:30 0 [Warning] Can't open and lock privilege tables: Table 'mysql.servers' doesn't exist\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:32 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '0.0.0.0', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:32 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '::', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:32 0 [ERROR] Fatal error: Can't open and lock privilege tables: Table 'mysql.db' doesn't exist\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan mariadbd[1389]: 2026-06-07 13:19:32 0 [ERROR] Aborting\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39mmariadb.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=1/FAILURE\u001b[0m\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;33m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mmariadb.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.\u001b[0m\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31mFailed to start MariaDB 12.3.2 database server.\u001b[0m\r\nJun 07 13:19:32 advan systemd[1]: mariadb.service: Consumed 2.498s CPU time over 2.726s wall clock time, 94.1M memory peak.\r\n"]
